                              value must be used strictly within a speech block (sp).</desc>
                        </valItem>
                        <valItem ident="acting">
                           <desc>Describes non-verbal physical performance, gestures, or facial
                              expressions; typically used as independent directions outside of a
                              speech block.</desc>
                        </valItem>
                        <valItem ident="entrance">
