                              position on the set.</desc>
                        </valItem>
                        <valItem ident="timing">
                           <desc>Indicates dramatic rhythm, pauses, or 'beats' within the
                              action.</desc>
                        </valItem>
                        <valItem ident="address">
                           <desc>Used when a character addresses the audience or camera directly,
                              breaking the fourth wall.</desc>
                        </valItem>
                     </valList>
                  </attDef>
               </attList>
               <exemplum>
